          "name": "Sebastien Buisson",
          "email": "sebastien.buisson@bull.net",
          "date": "2013-04-11 11:47:19.000000000",
          "tz": 120
        },
        "subject": "LU-3023 build: fix fuzzy logic in get_root_path()",
        "message": "LU-3023 build: fix fuzzy logic in get_root_path()\n\nThanks to the call to llapi_is_lustre_mnt(), we are sure that\nmnt.mnt_fsname contains \":/\".\nAnd, if no other mountpoint is found (len ==0), there is no reason\nto abort scanning, so the check and -EINVAL can just be removed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sebastien.buisson@bull.net>\nChange-Id: Id77c41fbf53782d657034f152f724a3bdc83408c\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
